name: floss
desc: Floss is a vector graphics abstraction library for Flutter.

name: Arc
desc: A canvas operation for drawing an arc.

name: Arc
desc:
Create an Arc is defined by a rect, startAngle, sweepAngle, and
optionally a paint object for styling and optionally whether to use the
rect center.

name: Atlas
desc: An atlas for rendering images on a canvas.

name: Atlas
desc: Creates a new Atlas instance.

name: BackgroundPicture
desc:
A drawing operation that draws a background picture on the canvas. Used for
the NoClearCanvas configuration.

name: BackgroundPicture
desc: Creates a new BackgroundPicture instance with the specified size.

name: BackgroundPictureType
desc: A background picture type.

name: CanvasOp
desc: A sealed class for performing various canvas operations.

name: draw
desc: Draws this CanvasOp on the provided canvas.

name: CanvasPictureType
desc: A picture type that uses a ui.Picture object.

name: Circle
desc: A canvas operation for drawing a circle.

name: Circle
desc:
Creates a Circle defined by its center point center, radius, and
paint.

name: ClearCanvas
desc: Represents a clear canvas configuration.

name: ClearCanvasType
desc: Represents a sealed class for clearing the canvas.

name: ClipPath
desc: Clips the drawing operations that compose the class with a path.

name: ClipPath
desc:
Creates a new ClipPath instance with the specified path and optionally
whether to use anti-aliasing.

name: ClipRRect
desc:
Clips the drawing operations that compose the class with a rounded
rectangle.

name: ClipRRect
desc:
Creates a new ClipRRect instance with the specified rrect and
optionally whether to use anti-aliasing.

name: ClipRect
desc: Clips the drawing operations that compose the class with a rectangle.

name: ClipRect
desc:
Creates a new ClipRect instance with the specified rect, clipOp, and
optionally whether to use anti-aliasing.

name: Color
desc: A color and blend mode to be applied to the entire canvas.

name: Color
desc: Creates a Color instance with the specified color and blendMode.

name: Config
desc: Represents a FlossWidget configuration for a specific model type.

name: DRRect
desc:
A canvas operation for drawing the difference between two rounded
rectangles.

name: DRRect
desc:
Creates a DRRect instance with the specified outer and inner,
ui.RRect, and paint.

name: DoubleTap
desc: Represents a double tap event.

name: DoubleTapCancel
desc: Represents a double tap cancel event.

name: DoubleTapDown
desc: Represents a double tap down event.

name: Drawing
desc:
A sealed class for composite canvas drawing operations. Meant to be used for
operations that should be applied to all CanvasOps composing this drawing
type.

name: Drawing
desc: Creates a new Drawing instance with the specified ops.

name: draw
desc: Draws this Drawing on the provided canvas.

name: walk
desc: Walks the drawing tree and yields each Drawing in the tree.

name: Fill
desc: A canvas operation for filling the canvas with a paint object.

name: Fill
desc: Creates a Fill instance with the specified paint.

name: FlossWidget
desc: A widget that provides a canvas for drawing.

name: FlossWidget
desc: Creates a new FlossWidget instance.

name: createState
desc: Creates the mutable state for this widget at a given location in the tree.

name: ForcePressEnd
desc: Represents a force press end event.

name: ForcePressPeak
desc: Represents a force press peak event.

name: ForcePressStart
desc: Represents a force press start event.

name: ForcePressUpdate
desc: Represents a force press update event.

name: ICanvasOp
desc: A interface for canvas operations.

name: Image
desc: A canvas operation for drawing an image.

name: Image
desc:
Creates an Image instance with the specified image, offset, and
paint.

name: ImageNine
desc: A canvas operation for drawing a nine-patch image.

name: ImageNine
desc:
Creates an ImageNine instance with the specified image, center,
dst, and paint.

name: ImageRect
desc:
A canvas operation for drawing an rectangular section of an image to the
canvas.

name: ImageRect
desc:
Creates an ImageRect instance with the specified image, src, dst,
and paint.

name: InputEvent
desc: Represents an input event.

name: InputEventList
desc: Represents a list of input events.

name: add
desc: Adds an input event to the list.

name: clear
desc: Clears the list of input events.

name: iterator
desc: A new Iterator that allows iterating the elements of this Iterable.

name: Iud
desc:
An interface for the init, update, draw, dispose and
onExitRequested methods.

name: dispose
desc: Disposes of any resources held by the model.

name: draw
desc: Draws the model on the canvas.

name: init
desc:
Initializes the model using the modelCtor, size, and
inputEvents.

name: onExitRequested
desc: Called when the user requests to exit the application.

name: update
desc: Updates the model using the elapsed, size, and inputEvents.

name: IudBase
desc: A base class for the Iud interface.

name: dispose
desc: Default implementation of the dispose method.

name: draw
desc: Default implementation of the draw method.

name: init
desc: Default implementation of the init method.

name: onExitRequested
desc: Default implementation of the onExitRequested method.

name: update
desc: Default implementation of the update method.

name: KeyEvent
desc: Represents a key event.

desc: Represents an input event when a pointer hovers over a target.

name: NoClearCanvas
desc: Represents a type of canvas that does not clear itself before drawing.

name: Noop
desc:
A drawing operation that does nothing. Useful in scenarios where a branch
decides which of two drawings to use and one of the branches should do
nothing.

desc: Creates a new Noop instance.

name: clampLen
desc:
Returns an Offset in the same direction but with a length
clamped to maxLength (if the current length exceeds it).

name: norm
desc:
Returns the unit vector in the same direction as this Offset.
If the Offset is zero-length, returns Offset.zero.
